HEADWORD: Tetterwort
<hw>Tet"ter*wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant used as a remedy for tetter, -- in England the calendine,
in America the bloodroot.</def>⟦br⟧
